org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.processing

Class UnboundMessageProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.processing.MessageProcessorBase
      • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.processing.UnboundMessageProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Runnable, MessageSource, MessageProcessor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IsolationMessageProcessor, NonBlockingMessageProcessor

    public abstract class UnboundMessageProcessor
extends MessageProcessorBase
    Common code for NonBlockingMessageProcessor and IsolationMessageProcessor, which are not bound to a thread.

    UnboundMessageProcessor supports thread migration only between instances of this class.
